Note: This prompt is designed for an AI development tool to generate a complete, production-ready Landing Page and Public Developer Docs for LifeOps. It enforces runtime safety rules: guard all array operations and API responses against null/undefined, initialize state with proper array/object defaults, and validate API shapes. Follow the styling system provided in PROJECT CONTEXT.

